name: renaissance(mashup)
description:
a mashup of Raphael’s Saint Catherine of Alexandria and Rembrandt’s Self-Portrait with Two Circles, along these rules:

1. if random(1) is greater than 0.5 then use an unaltered square from Raphael’s painting
2. if random(1) is smaller than 0.5 then use the hue of Raphael’s painting but with the saturation and brightness of Rembrandt’s painting
